-<HEAD>§ 54.601   Health care provider eligibility.</HEAD>
-<P>(a) <I>Eligible health care providers.</I> (1) Only an entity that is either a public or non-profit health care provider, as defined in this subpart, shall be eligible to receive support under this subpart.
