-<P>(b) <I>Inside wiring/internal connections.</I> Expenses associated with inside wiring or internal connections are ineligible for support under the Healthcare Connect Fund.
-</P>
-<P>(c) <I>Administrative expenses.</I> Administrative expenses are not eligible for support under the Healthcare Connect Fund.
